<p>
  Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,
</p>

<p>
  Thanks for uploading your first .blend file to Blendergrid!
</p>

<p>
  The next step is to calculate the price of your project. It's free, and it
  does two useful things at once: you'll see exactly what your render will
  cost, and Blendergrid generates a few preview renders so you can confirm
  everything looks right before paying for the full job.
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= projects_url(session_token: @session_token) %>"
     style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 22px; background: #101828;
            color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;">
    Calculate your price
  </a>
</p>

<p>
  Any questions? Just hit reply, we're happy to help :)
</p>

<p>
  Happy rendering,<br>
  the Blendergrid team
</p>

<p>
  <a href="https://www.blendergrid.com">www.blendergrid.com</a>
</p>
